{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ideececdf0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1562"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1562"},"text":"§ 1562.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" False representations as certified seed; required provisions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Any labeling, advertisement, or other representation subject to this chapter which represents that any seed is certified seed or any class thereof shall be deemed to be false in this respect unless (a) it has been determined by a seed certifying agency that such seed conformed to standards of genetic purity and identity as to kind or variety, and is in compliance with the rules and regulations of such agency pertaining to such seed; and (b) the seed bears an official label issued for such seed by a seed certifying agency certifying that the seed is of a specified class and a specified kind or variety. Seed of a variety for which a certificate of plant variety protection under the Plant Variety Protection Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2321"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 2321","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] specifies sale only as a class of certified seed shall be certified only when"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideececdf1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1562/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the basic seed from which the variety was produced furnished by authority of the owner of the variety if the certification is made during the term of protection, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideececdf2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1562/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" it conforms to the number of generations designated by the certificate, if the certificate contains such a designation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ideececdf3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1939-08-09/ch615"},"text":"Aug. 9, 1939, ch. 615","children":[],"tail":", title I, § 102, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/85/581/s4"},"text":"Pub. L. 85–581, § 4","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1958-08-01"},"text":"Aug. 1, 1958","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/72/476"},"text":"72 Stat. 476","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/89/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–89, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1969","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/83/134"},"text":"83 Stat. 134","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/577/tIII/s142/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–577, title III, § 142(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-24"},"text":"Dec. 24, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1558"},"text":"84 Stat. 1558","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ideececdf4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ideececdf5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"ideececdf6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Plant Variety Protection Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–577","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-24"},"text":"Dec. 24, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1542"},"text":"84 Stat. 1542","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 57 (§ 2321 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2321"},"text":"section 2321 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ideececdf7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1970—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–577","children":[],"tail":" inserted provisions setting out conditions for certification of seed of any variety for which a certificate of plant variety protection under the Plant Variety Protection Act specifies sale only as a class of certified seed."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1969—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/89"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–89","children":[],"tail":" struck out references to registered seed, and required labels, advertisement, or other representations to certify that the seed contained therein was determined by a seed certifying agency to be of a specified class and a specified kind of variety in conformity with the standards of genetic purity and identity as to kind or variety."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"ideececdf8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"ideececdf9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1970 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–577","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-24"},"text":"Dec. 24, 1970","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/577/s141"},"text":"section 141 of Pub. L. 91–577","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2321"},"text":"section 2321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
